msgid "It is the heart of the Linux system."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '    * '
#: ../src/docs/books/admin_guide/01-presentation.md:125
msgid "It manages the hardware resources of the system."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '    * '
#: ../src/docs/books/admin_guide/01-presentation.md:125
msgid ""
"The other software components must go through it to access the hardware."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '* '
#: ../src/docs/books/admin_guide/01-presentation.md:125
msgid ""
"The **shell** is a utility that interprets user commands and ensures their "
"execution."
